      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS STAR LEE (3) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (17.83) behind Just A Favour at Mandurah. Makes plenty of appeal. CHAROS FINALE (4) turned in a moderate performance last time when fifth at this track over 297m behind Fire Up Frog (18.03) in a Novice race. Was a winner prior to that. Should play a prominent role. ALISON'S MISSION (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (18.30) in a Novice race at this track. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Cannot be taken lightly. MAKUTZ (2) is right in the mix.",
